<p><img src="https://csuxjmfbwmkxiegfpljm.supabase.co/storage/v1/object/public/blog-images/organization-24002/1775292732524_IT-expert-wiring-peer-to-peer-AI-setup.jpeg" alt="IT expert wiring peer-to-peer AI setup"></p>
